{"tid":1032140,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"求救 隔離屋剪左我屋企上網線！！！","createTime":"2019-02-22T06:55:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T10:38:35.000Z","uid":128828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2c8589d08bb38d269a3dc6bf373de1c9c42eb56e","tid":1032140,"uid":128828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T06:55:43.000Z","msg":"話說前幾日隔離屋唔知係轉上網公司 定轉光鑯之類<br />\n之後個晚就開始上唔到網 今日call左師傅上黎我屋企睇<br />\n師傅見唔對路 就走去樓層到睇 <br />\n原來我屋企條線比人剪撚斷左 要拉過條新線入屋重新接駁返先用得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打比管理處又話佢唔可以管呢d野<br />\n打佢隔離屋用個間上網公司(x港x頻)又話要check下先，佢都唔知咩事咁話就算數<br />\n<br />\n乜自己裝上網線既時候可以剪鳩人地條線？？<br />\n然後可以不了了之？？<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打試過發生呢種情況，可以點做？？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"856d2c6fe0c946ffae43d909fa9329d2e74ac959","tid":1032140,"uid":222052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T06:56:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"057b61987c72c08e1310c76998a60defd733d336","tid":1032140,"uid":222767,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T06:56:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"011ec4a17768d98755b11c6a425b46c365a04a84","tid":1032140,"uid":217010,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T06:57:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e2230043c57dd109f6f401930e01c62d119def0","tid":1032140,"uid":215797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T09:40:22.000Z","msg":"剪鳩番佢條線"},{"pid":"a2bcf7c1e243a05b567d4080983de075f24f9e76","tid":1032140,"uid":176835,"